---
title: Melted Mozzarella Beef Mince with baby spinach and roasted potatoes
description: Though these may be Italian style meatballs, they're made with 100% Irish beef. Accompanied by a side of crispy roast potatoes and topped with melted mozzarella, this is a dish that everyone's sure to love.
